Date: 1997-04-30

Title: Form-factors of exponential fields in the affine A^{(1)}_{N-1} Toda

modelComments: 12 pages, harvmac.tex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B408 (1997) 192-200

A free field representation for form-factors of exponential operators in theaffine A^{(1)}_{N-1} Toda model is proposed. The one and two particleform-factors are calculated explicitly.